The company, together with its subsidiaries, is the largest Italian discount store with more than 1,100 stores in Italy and Slovenia. It strives to strengthen its leadership in Italy and become one of the most significant companies in Europe, maintaining consistently low prices with quality products. As a holding company, it provides group planning and strategy. In particular, the company also exercises financial control over its subsidiaries, settles their general policy and appoints their top managements, as well as provides central services.
